channel.title: I got 5K plays on my soundcloud page!
channel.description:
![41%20PM|339x110](upload://bRcfmASjL5luXju8W5DgDiD42Nl.png)
today I reached 5,000 plays aaaaaaaa. just wanna quickly say thank you to all you guys who truly support me, couldnt ask for anyone better to listen and appreciate my music (even if it is weird :P )
thanks for being one the best music communities ive experienced.
peace. -noah // DPWG
